CONTROLS:

a - left
d - right
space - jump
left arrow - pan left
right arrow - pan right
up arrow - pan up
down arrow - pan down
plus key - zoom in
minus key - zoom out
multiply key - back to original zoom
mouse button press to push ball in that direction
q - quit window


BONUS:
I have created another frame with another pool. I have implemented friction on ground and reflection  off walls.
I have changed the background theme after an interval. Moving porcupines is also a feature. Score displayed on Window header.
I have added music to the game as well.

----------------------------------------------------------

Running The Game:

Create a build directory inside graphics-boilerplate
cmake .. inside build
make all inside build 
run executable inside build --> ./graphics-asgn1
